Belief_State.Axiom:
**Built-in observability.** Every task contains an `Execution Log` section where the execution agent records every meaningful action, especially:
- executed verification commands (with exit code and pass/fail);
- confirmed scenario-to-test pairs (file::case);
- **introduction of new entities**: the wording `Introduced  because ` is mandatory for every entity not listed in the corresponding domain's Entity Inventory. This feeds the subsequent audit.

**`DONE` is a proven fact.** The Completion Rule in every ticket is worded so the execution agent cannot honestly close a task until:
- verification commands have been executed;
- scenario-to-test coverage has been confirmed;
- deferred scope (if any) has been recorded;
- all entities introduced outside inventory have been logged.

Step.Action:
